{
  "title": "About Us - Shikshanam",
  "content": "<main class=\"main-container py-16\"><div class=\"max-w-4xl mx-auto\"><div class=\"text-center mb-16\"><h1 class=\"text-4xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">About Shikshanam</h1><p class=\"text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-3xl mx-auto\">We are dedicated to preserving and sharing the timeless wisdom of ancient India through modern technology and innovative learning methods.</p></div><div class=\"grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 mb-16\"><div><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">Our Mission</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Shikshanam was born from a deep reverence for India&#x27;s ancient knowledge systems. We believe that the wisdom of Sanskrit, Darshanas, and traditional self-help practices holds the key to personal growth and spiritual development in the modern world.</p><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6\">Our mission is to make this profound knowledge accessible to everyone, regardless of their background or location, through carefully crafted courses, interactive tools, and expert guidance.</p><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-saffron-50 to-peacock-green-50 rounded-2xl p-6\"><h3 class=\"text-lg font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Our Vision</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">To create a global community of learners who embrace ancient wisdom for modern living, fostering personal growth, cultural understanding, and spiritual development.</p></div></div><div class=\"bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6\">What We Offer</h2><div class=\"space-y-4\"><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-saffron-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-saffron-600 rounded-full\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Sanskrit Learning</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\">Comprehensive courses from beginner to advanced levels</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-saffron-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-saffron-600 rounded-full\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Darshan Studies</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\">Deep exploration of Indian philosophical systems</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-saffron-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-saffron-600 rounded-full\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Self-Help Wisdom</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\">Ancient practices for modern personal development</p></div></div><div class=\"flex items-start space-x-3\"><div class=\"w-6 h-6 bg-saffron-100 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mt-1\"><div class=\"w-2 h-2 bg-saffron-600 rounded-full\"></div></div><div><h3 class=\"font-semibold text-gray-900\">Expert Guidance</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600 text-sm\">Learn from experienced scholars and practitioners</p></div></div></div></div></div><div class=\"mb-16\"><h2 class=\"text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 text-center mb-12\">Our Values</h2><div class=\"grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8\"><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-saffron-500 to-peacock-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M12 6.253v13m0-13C10.832 5.477 9.246 5 7.5 5S4.168 5.477 3 6.253v13C4.168 18.477 5.754 18 7.5 18s3.332.477 4.5 1.253m0-13C13.168 5.477 14.754 5 16.5 5c1.746 0 3.332.477 4.5 1.253v13C19.832 18.477 18.246 18 16.5 18c-1.746 0-3.332.477-4.5 1.253\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Authenticity</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">We maintain the highest standards of authenticity in our teachings, ensuring that ancient wisdom is preserved and transmitted accurately.</p></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-saffron-500 to-peacock-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M17 20h5v-2a3 3 0 00-5.356-1.857M17 20H7m10 0v-2c0-.656-.126-1.283-.356-1.857M7 20H2v-2a3 3 0 015.356-1.857M7 20v-2c0-.656.126-1.283.356-1.857m0 0a5.002 5.002 0 019.288 0M15 7a3 3 0 11-6 0 3 3 0 016 0zm6 3a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0zM7 10a2 2 0 11-4 0 2 2 0 014 0z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Community</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">We foster a supportive learning community where students can connect, share experiences, and grow together on their spiritual journey.</p></div><div class=\"text-center\"><div class=\"w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-saffron-500 to-peacock-green-500 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4\"><svg class=\"w-8 h-8 text-white\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\"><path stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-width=\"2\" d=\"M13 10V3L4 14h7v7l9-11h-7z\"></path></svg></div><h3 class=\"text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-3\">Innovation</h3><p class=\"text-gray-600\">We combine traditional wisdom with modern technology to create engaging, effective learning experiences for the digital age.</p></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-saffron-50 to-peacock-green-50 rounded-2xl p-8 text-center\"><h2 class=\"text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4\">Join Our Journey</h2><p class=\"text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-2xl mx-auto\">Whether you&#x27;re a complete beginner or an advanced practitioner, Shikshanam offers a path for everyone to explore and embrace the wisdom of ancient India.</p><div class=\"flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center\"><a href=\"/courses\" class=\"bg-gradient-to-r from-saffron-600 to-saffron-700 hover:from-saffron-700 hover:to-saffron-800 text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300 transform hover:scale-105 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl\">Explore Courses</a><a href=\"/contact\" class=\"border-2 border-saffron-600 text-saffron-700 hover:bg-saffron-600 hover:text-white font-semibold py-3 px-8 rounded-2xl transition-all duration-300\">Get in Touch</a></div></div></div>",
